{
  "cacheVersion": "2026-05-13-gear-cards",
  "html": "<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"date-2025-03-10t151648-04modified-2025-03-17t132312-04\">date: 2025-03-10T15:16:48-04<div class=\"\"></div>\nmodified: 2025-03-17T13:23:12-04<div class=\"\"></div></h2>\n<p class=\"\">Been experimenting with a smallweb-powered mini-app generator called smallbot, but ran into some bugs with write permissions</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Smallbot AI assistant successfully created a minimal 37-character Hello World HTML application after two failed permission attempts.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741706866/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_11.27.32_AM.png\" alt=\"Smallbot AI assistant successfully created a minimal 37-character Hello World HTML application after two failed permission attempts.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1741706866/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_11.27.32_AM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1741706866/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_11.27.32_AM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741706866/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_11.27.32_AM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1741706866/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_11.27.32_AM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Smallbot AI assistant successfully created a minimal 37-character Hello World HTML application after two failed permission attempts.\" width=\"3348\" height=\"2486\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.63deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3348×2486\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Smallbot AI assistant successfully created a minimal 37-character Hello World HTML application after two failed permission attempts.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\">Experimented with capturing photos of a bunch of differrent mouth positions and using Adobe Character Animator to sync them to audio</p>\n<p class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741725178/Screen_Recording_2025-03-11_at_4.31.51_PM.gif\" alt=\"Screenshot - 2025-03-11 16:33 - Screen Recording 2025-03-11 at 4.31.51 PM.mov\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1741725178/Screen_Recording_2025-03-11_at_4.31.51_PM.gif 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1741725178/Screen_Recording_2025-03-11_at_4.31.51_PM.gif 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741725178/Screen_Recording_2025-03-11_at_4.31.51_PM.gif 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1741725178/Screen_Recording_2025-03-11_at_4.31.51_PM.gif 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" style=\"--splay-rot:-1.92deg;\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></p>\n<p class=\"\">Worked on some visualizations, full project at <a href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20251008002106/https://para-leaks.ejfox.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\" data-preview-url=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20251008002106/https://para-leaks.ejfox.com\">http://web.archive.org/web/20251008002106/https://para-leaks.ejfox.com<svg class=\"inline-block w-4 h-4 ml-1 opacity-50 dark:opacity-75 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity align-text-bottom\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.88em\" height=\"1em\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M393.674 430.14V448H54.326l.004-17.86zm-13.395-26.791v22.325H67.721V403.35zM100.452 162.233l3.726 1.883l1.864 30.11l1.865 48.928v47.055l-1.865 58.656l-.31 39.515l-5.28 1.573H81.816l-5.59-1.573l-2.172-39.515l-1.868-58.343v-47.051l1.868-49.244l1.704-30.273l3.887-1.721zm267.909 0l3.73 1.883l1.861 30.11l1.862 48.928v47.055l-1.862 58.656l-.306 39.515l-5.285 1.573h-18.636l-5.592-1.573l-2.179-39.515l-1.861-58.343v-47.051l1.861-49.244l1.712-30.273l3.884-1.721zm-187.538 0l3.726 1.883l1.865 30.11l1.865 48.928v47.055l-1.865 58.656l-.307 39.515l-5.284 1.573h-18.638l-5.594-1.573l-2.172-39.515l-1.86-58.343v-47.051l1.86-49.244l1.712-30.273l3.88-1.721zm102.698 0l3.726 1.883l1.865 30.11l1.865 48.928v47.055l-1.865 58.656l-.307 39.515l-5.284 1.573h-18.638l-5.59-1.573l-2.176-39.515l-1.861-58.343v-47.051l1.861-49.244l1.712-30.273l3.883-1.721zm96.758-40.186v31.255H67.721v-31.255ZM220.785 64l163.96 37.546l-6.574 11.57H64.15l-9.823-9.383z\" class=\"\"></path></svg></a></p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Stacked area chart tracking message volume from five senders (Unknown, Deleted Account, Ed, Coop, John/Nat.Cmd) from January 2021 through January 2024, showing peak activity in early 2022 with sharp decline thereafter.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741747447/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_10.43.55_PM.png\" alt=\"Stacked area chart tracking message volume from five senders (Unknown, Deleted Account, Ed, Coop, John/Nat.Cmd) from January 2021 through January 2024, showing peak activity in early 2022 with sharp decline thereafter.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1741747447/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_10.43.55_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1741747447/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_10.43.55_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741747447/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_10.43.55_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1741747447/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_10.43.55_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Stacked area chart tracking message volume from five senders (Unknown, Deleted Account, Ed, Coop, John/Nat.Cmd) from January 2021 through January 2024, showing peak activity in early 2022 with sharp decline thereafter.\" width=\"2118\" height=\"812\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"2118×812\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Stacked area chart tracking message volume from five senders (Unknown, Deleted Account, Ed, Coop, John/Nat.Cmd) from January 2021 through January 2024, showing peak activity in early 2022 with sharp decline thereafter.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Stacked area chart tracking message volume from multiple senders from January 2021 to 2024, with Unknown sender dominating most periods and Z sender surging dramatically in early 2024.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741750272/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_11.31.00_PM.png\" alt=\"Stacked area chart tracking message volume from multiple senders from January 2021 to 2024, with Unknown sender dominating most periods and Z sender surging dramatically in early 2024.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1741750272/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_11.31.00_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1741750272/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_11.31.00_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741750272/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_11.31.00_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1741750272/Screenshot_2025-03-11_at_11.31.00_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Stacked area chart tracking message volume from multiple senders from January 2021 to 2024, with Unknown sender dominating most periods and Z sender surging dramatically in early 2024.\" width=\"2138\" height=\"1186\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"2138×1186\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Stacked area chart tracking message volume from multiple senders from January 2021 to 2024, with Unknown sender dominating most periods and Z sender surging dramatically in early 2024.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\">Weird practice flights from poughkeepsie lately</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"FlightRadar24 tracking US Air Force C-17 Globemaster cargo plane en route to Poughkeepsie with live position on eastern US map.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741799120/Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_1.04.58_PM.png\" alt=\"FlightRadar24 tracking US Air Force C-17 Globemaster cargo plane en route to Poughkeepsie with live position on eastern US map.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1741799120/Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_1.04.58_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1741799120/Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_1.04.58_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741799120/Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_1.04.58_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1741799120/Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_1.04.58_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"FlightRadar24 tracking US Air Force C-17 Globemaster cargo plane en route to Poughkeepsie with live position on eastern US map.\" width=\"3600\" height=\"2338\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.02deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3600×2338\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">FlightRadar24 tracking US Air Force C-17 Globemaster cargo plane en route to Poughkeepsie with live position on eastern US map.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Streamed message volume trends from 1,108 senders over three years, with Animal TN State and Perdue/Hawk/CRVO as top contributors.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741804220/Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_2.30.07_PM.png\" alt=\"Streamed message volume trends from 1,108 senders over three years, with Animal TN State and Perdue/Hawk/CRVO as top contributors.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1741804220/Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_2.30.07_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1741804220/Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_2.30.07_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1741804220/Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_2.30.07_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1741804220/Screenshot_2025-03-12_at_2.30.07_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Streamed message volume trends from 1,108 senders over three years, with Animal TN State and Perdue/Hawk/CRVO as top contributors.\" width=\"1670\" height=\"1206\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.98deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1670×1206\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Streamed message volume trends from 1,108 senders over three years, with Animal TN State and Perdue/Hawk/CRVO as top contributors.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Mind map connecting occult and technological concepts, linking Elder Gods and algorithms as parallel systems of power and knowledge.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742068749/Screenshot_2025-03-15_at_3.58.44_PM.png\" alt=\"Mind map connecting occult and technological concepts, linking Elder Gods and algorithms as parallel systems of power and knowledge.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1742068749/Screenshot_2025-03-15_at_3.58.44_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1742068749/Screenshot_2025-03-15_at_3.58.44_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742068749/Screenshot_2025-03-15_at_3.58.44_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1742068749/Screenshot_2025-03-15_at_3.58.44_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Mind map connecting occult and technological concepts, linking Elder Gods and algorithms as parallel systems of power and knowledge.\" width=\"1462\" height=\"1034\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.57deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1462×1034\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Mind map connecting occult and technological concepts, linking Elder Gods and algorithms as parallel systems of power and knowledge.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742076644/Screen_Recording_2025-03-15_at_6.08.32_PM.mov\" alt=\"Screenshot - 2025-03-15 18:10 - Screen Recording 2025-03-15 at 6.08.32 PM.mov\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1742076644/Screen_Recording_2025-03-15_at_6.08.32_PM.mov 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1742076644/Screen_Recording_2025-03-15_at_6.08.32_PM.mov 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742076644/Screen_Recording_2025-03-15_at_6.08.32_PM.mov 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1742076644/Screen_Recording_2025-03-15_at_6.08.32_PM.mov 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" style=\"--splay-rot:-1.53deg;\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></p>\n<p class=\"\">I continue to reduce my FPV flight times!</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Flight simulation game results showing ejfox&#x27;s current time of 1.661 ranking first, with personal best times for gold (0.000), silver (0.000), and bronze (1.000) medals displayed.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742095176/Screenshot_2025-03-15_at_11.19.19_PM.png\" alt=\"Flight simulation game results showing ejfox&#x27;s current time of 1.661 ranking first, with personal best times for gold (0.000), silver (0.000), and bronze (1.000) medals displayed.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1742095176/Screenshot_2025-03-15_at_11.19.19_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1742095176/Screenshot_2025-03-15_at_11.19.19_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742095176/Screenshot_2025-03-15_at_11.19.19_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1742095176/Screenshot_2025-03-15_at_11.19.19_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Flight simulation game results showing ejfox&#x27;s current time of 1.661 ranking first, with personal best times for gold (0.000), silver (0.000), and bronze (1.000) medals displayed.\" width=\"3600\" height=\"2338\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.43deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3600×2338\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Flight simulation game results showing ejfox's current time of 1.661 ranking first, with personal best times for gold (0.000), silver (0.000), and bronze (1.000) medals displayed.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\">Worked on scheduling out some YouTube videos so I can spend more time working on them and refining them.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"SmallWeb VPS Edition product box with text about setting up apps quickly and making them accessible to friends.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742153201/Screenshot_2025-03-16_at_3.26.32_PM.png\" alt=\"SmallWeb VPS Edition product box with text about setting up apps quickly and making them accessible to friends.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1742153201/Screenshot_2025-03-16_at_3.26.32_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1742153201/Screenshot_2025-03-16_at_3.26.32_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742153201/Screenshot_2025-03-16_at_3.26.32_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1742153201/Screenshot_2025-03-16_at_3.26.32_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"SmallWeb VPS Edition product box with text about setting up apps quickly and making them accessible to friends.\" width=\"776\" height=\"434\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.19deg;\" data-dimensions=\"776×434\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">SmallWeb VPS Edition product box with text about setting up apps quickly and making them accessible to friends.</figcaption>\n</figure>",
